item.title: CVE-2024-5968|2024-10-09T06:00:05.106Z -- unknown -- photo%20gallery%20by%2010web
item.description: The Photo Gallery by 10Web WordPress plugin before 1.8.28 does not properly sanitise and escape some of its Gallery settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
